    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1890-08-25T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1890-08-25T00:00:00-05:00" n="73" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d73">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Mizner</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Blaine</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of
                                    the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Guatemala</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1890-08-25">
                            <hi rend="italic">August</hi> 25,
                            1890</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Mizner reports the nonagreement of Salvador to the bases of peace and the
                        extension of the time 4 days by the Government of Guatemala.</p>
            </div>
